{"tid":1568644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家藍絲同我哋最大分別係","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:10:50.000Z","uid":215829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c30930c6c78972e019ba3c54cce8015bd263bc01","tid":1568644,"uid":215829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:40:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲有何君堯或其他組織領頭 引手足出黎 然後警犬拉人 <br />\n佢哋而家有組織 同警犬有默契<br />\n反觀 我哋由六月開始 因為冇大台 所以撐到咁耐 但係冇大台 令我哋好似一盤散沙 有分歧<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家要諗嘅係 如何係冇大台嘅原則底下 小心策劃行動 唔好一盤散沙 <br />\n<br />\n手足請集思廣益"},{"pid":"19ceac9eb895caaef805c5ac5fb4742bfa0f05aa","tid":1568644,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"我地都要有大台！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36df2f5a31c39650108a1c3364ad9e5751d1a577","tid":1568644,"uid":215829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19ceac9eb895caaef805c5ac5fb4742bfa0f05aa","tid":1568644,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"我地都要有大台！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"要諗大台以外嘅方式"},{"pid":"238388128954718f65b96708c5555ecca34f028a","tid":1568644,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"佢宜家玩到鳩拉"},{"pid":"99e9398dcde3889c6e243734ad991b2776299bef","tid":1568644,"uid":101963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲應該借力打力，順水推舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568616</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f276f23edc2d22a896e5179691fd628f5517ddff","tid":1568644,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"佢而家係後生就拉"},{"pid":"94b1a739e391fed28f90227d